node.text:
We wanted to share with you how Takes Two has really helped our relationship and how it can better yours as well. We share clips from our honeymoon and and chat about how we discovered @TakesTwoKolbe. The knowledge you gain from doing this with your partner is invaluable! Get your custom report at 
https://m.takestwo.com/arielauren

node.title: Back from our honeymoon and we’d love to share more about @takestwokolbe!

node.text:
Lauren and I took a trip to Maui’s Nakalele Blowhole and the amazing Noa from Zeb Films captured this and put together one incredible edit. 
Song - Favorite Place To Go 
by Layup

Come check out our place! We had fun putting everything together... still a work in progress but we love it so far. Thank you Wayfair for working on this design with us! Here’s a link to a lot of the pieces you’ll see in the video... http://bit.ly/ourwayfairregistry
